# =============================================================================
# .vercelignore — keep the Vercel upload small and the build deterministic.
# The web client (apps/web) is built from packages/* + apps/web only. Everything
# below is multi-GB local research data, caches, or docs that must NOT be
# uploaded (the CLI otherwise tried to upload the whole data/ tree and hit the
# 100 MB per-file limit).
# =============================================================================

# --- Datasets / raw audio / embedding caches / neural artifacts (multi-GB) ---
# Keep ONLY the 4 small derived model JSONs that the prebuild stages into the
# SPA, so a remote build still serves the real trained prior.
data/*
!data/processed
data/processed/*
!data/processed/signal-lab
data/processed/signal-lab/*
!data/processed/signal-lab/*.json

# --- Offline research harness (PyTorch training; not part of the web build) ---
research/

# --- Docs, worklogs, parallel review/research scratch ---
docs/
worklog/
parallel-agent-review/
parallel-research-pass/
.extract/
.pytest_cache/

# --- Logs and local scratch probes ---
*.log
_*.py
_*.txt
